<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Helia UV Support</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background: #EAF7FF;
      color: #1F2937;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 820px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 32px 18px 56px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #FFFFFF;
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 28px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 34px;
      margin: 0 0 8px;
    }

    h2 {
      margin-top: 28px;
      font-size: 23px;
    }

    h3 {
      margin-top: 22px;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    p, li {
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .muted {
      color: #6B7280;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .lang-switch {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #FFB627;
      color: #111827;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .secondary {
      background: #FFF8EE;
      border: 1px solid #F2D8A7;
    }

    .email {
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #2E617D;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      color: #6B7280;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    hr {
      border: 0;
      border-top: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
      margin: 32px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <main class="container">
    <section class="card">
      <h1>Helia UV Support</h1>
      <p class="muted">Support page for Helia UV</p>

      <p>
        This page provides support information for Helia UV in English and Italian.
      </p>

      <div class="lang-switch">
        <a class="button" href="#english">English</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="#italiano">Italiano</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="english" class="card">
      <h2>Support — English</h2>

      <p>
        Need help with Helia UV? You can contact support by email:
      </p>

      <p class="email">
        sparkling_princess@hotmail.it
      </p>

      <h3>What to include in your message</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>A short description of the issue.</li>
        <li>Your device model and iOS version.</li>
        <li>The app version you are using.</li>
        <li>Whether the issue is related to UV data, widgets, HealthKit, notifications, or Pro subscription.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Common support topics</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Location and UV data:</strong> make sure location permissions are enabled for Helia UV.</li>
        <li><strong>HealthKit / Time in Daylight:</strong> make sure Health permissions are enabled in iOS Settings → Health → Data Access & Devices.</li>
        <li><strong>Widgets:</strong> open Helia UV at least once after installing or updating the app, then add or refresh the widget.</li>
        <li><strong>Pro subscription:</strong> use the Restore Purchases button if you already purchased Helia UV Pro.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Medical disclaimer</h3>
      <p>
        Helia UV is not a medical device and does not provide medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Information shown in the app is for general informational purposes only.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section id="italiano" class="card">
      <h2>Assistenza — Italiano</h2>

      <p>
        Hai bisogno di aiuto con Helia UV? Puoi contattare l’assistenza via email:
      </p>

      <p class="email">
        sparkling_princess@hotmail.it
      </p>

      <h3>Cosa indicare nel messaggio</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Una breve descrizione del problema.</li>
        <li>Il modello del dispositivo e la versione iOS.</li>
        <li>La versione dell’app che stai utilizzando.</li>
        <li>Se il problema riguarda dati UV, widget, HealthKit, notifiche o abbonamento Pro.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Argomenti frequenti</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Posizione e dati UV:</strong> verifica che i permessi di localizzazione siano attivi per Helia UV.</li>
        <li><strong>HealthKit / Tempo alla luce del giorno:</strong> verifica che i permessi Salute siano attivi in Impostazioni iOS → Salute → Accesso ai dati e dispositivi.</li>
        <li><strong>Widget:</strong> apri Helia UV almeno una volta dopo l’installazione o l’aggiornamento, poi aggiungi o aggiorna il widget.</li>
        <li><strong>Abbonamento Pro:</strong> usa il pulsante Ripristina acquisti se hai già acquistato Helia UV Pro.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Avvertenza medica</h3>
      <p>
        Helia UV non è un dispositivo medico e non fornisce consigli medici, diagnosi o trattamenti. Le informazioni mostrate nell’app sono a scopo informativo generale.
      </p>
    </section>

    <footer>
      © 2026 Helia UV
    </footer>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
